title: The Secret of Margrave Manor.rar
description: Dusty drapes and ancient chandeliers dot the spooky Margrave Manor house. As Edwina Margrave, you must find your grandfather who`s been missing for ten years. Your only clue to his whereabouts is a strange door with an odd puzzle to unlock. In each room, collect hidden objects and view your strange medley in the collection room. Can you uncover The Secret of Margrave Manor and discover your family`s forgotten past?
